Package: autoplotly
Type: Package
Title: Automatic Generation of Interactive Plots for Popular Statistical Results
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Yuan", "Tang", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "terrytangyuan@gmail.com")
Description: This package provides functionalities to automatically generate interactive
             plot for many popular statistical results supported by ggfortify package with
             plotly.js <https://plot.ly/>  and ggplot2 <http://ggplot2.tidyverse.org/> style.
             The generated plot can also be easily extended using ggplot2 syntax while keeping
             the plot interactive.
License: Apache License 2.0
URL: https://github.com/terrytangyuan/autoplotly
BugReports: https://github.com/terrytangyuan/autoplotly/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1)
Imports:
    plotly,
    ggfortify
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Suggests:
    testthat,
    knitr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
